<HEADLINE> News Items from Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 2 (Xinhua) -- Following are news items from the
Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua in Hong Kong Saturday:

hke050218 -- Major Foreign Exchange Rates in Indonesia
hka050219 -- Urgent: HK Jetfoil with 236 on Board Hits Unknown
