Ten minutes before the latest quake, an earthquake of magnitude
4.3 also hit the same peninsula.
</P>
<P>
The peninsula has experienced a series of mild quakes since
April 20.
</P>
<P>
The region, dotted with hot spring resorts, was the site of
fairly strong quakes in March last year. 
