<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, May 3 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand National Party
has managed to retain its parliament seat for the Taranaki/King
Country electorate in the by-election held on Saturday, TV New
Zealand reported Sunday night.
</P>
<P>
