<HEADLINE> Dhaka's Raw Jute Export to Exceed 0.396m Tons </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, May 3 (Xinhua) -- Bangladesh's raw jute export may
exceed 2.2 million bales (396,000 tons) this year, said a press
release from the Bangladesh Jute Association (BJA) available here
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Up to April 15, 1998, the country had exported over 2 million
bales (360,000 tons) of raw jute, the release said.
</P>
