<P>
A Thai military official on the border said fighting in
Cambodian escalated on Saturday as Cambodian government forces
tried to seize hill 200 from the Khmer Rouge guerrillas.
</P>
<P>
Several artillery shells strayed across the border, forcing
Thai gunners to fire warning shots. 
</P>
